{"word":"G3661 - ὁμοθυμαδόν - homothymadón - hom-oth-oo-mad-on' - With one accord","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὁμοθυμαδόν</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">homothymadón</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hom-oth-oo-mad-on'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">With one accord</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஒருமனப்பட்டு - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"with one mind"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from a compound of the base of <a href=\"#/G3674 - ὁμοῦ - homoû - hom-oo'/3674\">G3674</a> and <a href=\"#/G2372 - θυμός - thymós - thoo-mos'/2372\">G2372</a>; <i>unanimously:</i> - with one accord (mind).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3661/3661\">G3661</a>, <a href=\"#/G3674/3674\">G3674</a>"}]}